                            </h2>
                        </div>

                        <div class="layer-slick1 animated visible-false" data-appear="slideInUp" data-delay="1600">
                            <a href="/Home/Shop" class="flex-c-m stext-101 cl0 size-101 bg1 bor1 hov-btn1 p-lr-15 trans-04">
                                Shop Now
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

